casebody.head_matter:
Vernon Montrell WEBSTER, Petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES
No. 18-7572
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit for further consideration in light of the decision of the Supreme Court of Wisconsin in United States v. Franklin , 2019 WI 64, 387 Wis. 2d 259, 928 N.W. 2d 545 (2019).
